    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i>In <i>Chante: Fortress of Spores,</i> you play as  an adventurous little fungus trying to save her circle of spores.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Chante on their Adventure! Explore, solve puzzles, defend, and expand your Circle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras/5693f40e0ec52b69718b5ee50cbcac05.avif?t=1768554595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras_big/5693f40e0ec52b69718b5ee50cbcac05.avif?t=1768554595 width=800 height=180 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your adventure takes place beneath the surface. Use your wits to solve various puzzles. Secrets may lie hidden just beyond the corner. Can you find them all? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, beware of lurking enemies and wild mushrooms as they are territorial and will attack on sight! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras/1a93efbdc8adf340512a88418226ed3f.avif?t=1768554595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras_big/1a93efbdc8adf340512a88418226ed3f.avif?t=1768554595 width=800 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources and utilize them to craft allies that can assist in defending your safe zone! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras/94dd7f81c45334372d60ce4a1a6db8d1.avif?t=1768554595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras_big/94dd7f81c45334372d60ce4a1a6db8d1.avif?t=1768554595 width=800 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ants are declaring war! Protect your territory from their onslaught with your reliable shovel and the aid of your strategically placed Mushroom allies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras/a25171d8da9bc28a95879c071dc61c8e.avif?t=1768554595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras_big/a25171d8da9bc28a95879c071dc61c8e.avif?t=1768554595 width=800 height=180 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gain strength by defeating powerful enemies! Evolve your mushroom  into mighty allies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>After the game's storyline is complete, you can continue to gather all the undiscovered collectibles, find all the mushroom types, and evolve as much as your heart desires!</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras/275e146dddfd8c41a62a133d278ce1f2.avif?t=1768554595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3190570/extras_big/275e146dddfd8c41a62a133d278ce1f2.avif?t=1768554595 width=800 height=180 /></span></p>",
